----------

For information on travel please consider LPNMR'09 "Getting to Potsdam" at
http://www.cs.uni-potsdam.de/lpnmr09/index.php?page=getting-to-potsdamand
for accommodation suggestions visit the LPNMR'09 accommodation web page at
http://www.cs.uni-potsdam.de/lpnmr09/index.php?page=accommodation.

